\b Requirements:\

\b0 \
To build Lix for Mac OS X, you'll need Apple's {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://developer.apple.com"}}{\fldrslt Developer Tools}} for Xcode. The game also requires two additional libraries:\
\
- enet 1.3 (1.3.1 will also work)\
- Allegro 4.4.1\
\
