\b Building in Xcode:\
\

\b0 Firstly, open 
\f2 \cf2 ./mac/xcode/LixMac.xcodeproj
\f0 \cf0 .\
\
\ul To build the game (client):\ulnone \
Select the "LixMac" target, and "Build and Run".\
\
\ul To build the server (with the frontend):\
\ulnone Change the target to "LixServer". (or lixserv if you only want the server executable and not the controller app), and "Build and Run".\
\
\ul To build the server (with just the server binary):\ulnone \
1. Change the target to "lixserv", and "Build and Run".\
2. Move ./mac/xcode/build/Debug/LixCore.framework to /Library/Frameworks.\
3. Make sure /usr/local/lib/liballeg.4.4.1.dylib exists.\
(note: this has not yet been tested, but it should work)\
\
